		<Relevance><![CDATA[/* Windows XP or Higher */ version of operating system >= "5.1"]]></Relevance>
		<Relevance><![CDATA[/* Exists MSSQL Server */ exists services "MSSQLSERVER"]]></Relevance>
		<Relevance><![CDATA[/* Exists sqlcmd */ exists tuple string items 0 of concatenations ", " of pathnames of files whose(name of it as lowercase contains "sqlcmd") of (folders it) of unique values of (it as trimmed string) of substrings separated by (";";":") of values of (variables "PATH" of it; (if (windows of operating system) then (x64 variables "PATH" of it) else NOTHINGS) ) of environments]]></Relevance>
